{"tid":432430,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"IT界討論區：走定唔走（18)","createTime":"2017-10-11T13:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T14:03:20.000Z","uid":55462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c78d9c3d56525d8ba332d63f29948071f4a52aef","tid":432430,"uid":55462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入左間新公間番左兩日 發現唔岩做係mainly support 少development, expect 係mainly development, 少support<br />\n<br />\n但我個title 係programmer, 想走， 老細話手上有好多development project 味搞得晒住，所以暫時味有development, 所以而家做緊d testing 野， 又要support 下 user 聽下電話咁<br />\n<br />\nd 同事都係聽電話support user, 得一兩個同事先寫緊program, 其他都係做緊testing, 同 document 野<br />\n<br />\n你點睇好 番左兩日想走 但聽manager 講完，都會睇下<br />\n<br />\n巴打點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連個system 都係買番黎，好多都係買<br />\n可能話將來有需要先要寫program, 所以先寫果d requirement, 而家都成個call center 咁 見到佢地瘋狂聽call 同expect 既野 有出入。<br />\n<br />\n連version control tool, framework 都冇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無VERSION CONTROL 即走啦<br />\n2017 啦好嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成條team 10幾個人 係得一兩個人寫緊c#, 其他同事就全部word 檔， excel, mon住vendor 個system 改成點，自己唔洗main, <br />\n<br />\n而p 仔requirement <a href=\"http://話要.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A9%B1%E8%A6%81.net&d=1n6oaH6qWKwhWnv5h3CmGNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ac89c0ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">話要.net</a> framework, 又冇話asp定vb<br />\n第一日番工只係比張call list 我 話support user好重要 pdf 檔，連裝development 既tool都冇話要裝定先，只係mon 住vendor 做成點，問過老細話手頭上有好多project hold 住左，味開得手development住，<br />\n又問過上司佢成年都係support user, 接call, printer 出事都搵我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n苦惱緊等唔等development 機會，定直接走人 再搵in house development<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290cc9b8ed93c2a8bfa80a27de2e2bdfd0e5c233","tid":432430,"uid":55462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"開定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da4c2d5d91ffef6c9795d6862b28c4742fc40b4","tid":432430,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"姐係咁 我開過好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7d95877bf281e0703059206e3cb402d4d00f72","tid":432430,"uid":55462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係咁 我開過好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5859ad4ff2a6adb8e5f32b776be6f0703e57055","tid":432430,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係咁 我開過好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor